text.tspan: There are some rotted clothes and old bones here.
"There is no exit until the seven words are said."
Light beam — wait until night for it to disappear
There are tracks here, leading east.
"Know this, that a man called Tarjan, thought by many to be
insane, head through wizardry powers proclaimed himself
a god. His image is locked in stone until made whole again."
"Thor is the greatest son of Odin."
